sub_title: Senior Account Manager - East EU at Maxicom IT Distrubution B.V.
summary:
Master of economics with 6+ years of experience as an Account manager in corporate division in one of the biggest banks in Croatia - Erste & Steiermarkische bank. Experienced in sales of complex financial products, client management and strategic planning. Exceptionally dedicated professional with great interpersonal communication and organizational skills. Proven talent for aligning business strategy and objectives with established business development and sales management goals to achieve maximum operational impacts. 

Professional focal points include relationship management, market and financial analysis, KYC, negotiation, upselling and cross-selling, risk management and process improvement. Loves working in teams, but also knows to stand up for his own ideas. Curious person who embraces diversity and change. 

Described by colleagues as a progressive, driven, down-to-earth, precise, analytical, strategic, and managerial expert who can be relied on to offer solutions that deliver results on time. Looking for new challenges in a competitive and innovative market such as Netherlands.
